    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
        <title>SYSTEM HOSES</title>
        <para>Hoses used with air conditioning systems are nylon barrier type hoses This type of hose prevents the
            refrigerant from escaping through the walls of the hose into the atmosphere. When servicing air conditioning
            systems, use only replacement hoses approved for air conditioning systems.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
